# ArtifactGraph

- Product registries, templates, lexicons, and config are repository-local SSOT.
- Use local analyze/grill/parity/suggest before requesting cloud work.
- Never dump full registries or lexicons into `cloudPromptSlice`.
- Run only generation keys allowlisted by the current repo.
- Promote reviewed artifacts in the product repo, then rebuild the local index.
- Do not depend on `platform-repos.json`, `base-docs`, or `base-tests`.

Hooks: `.cursor/extracts/artifactgraph-hooks-core.md`
